    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Literature, stories, and oral traditions having to do with the beginnings of a culture, civilization, peoples, land, deity, hero, or other entity; often associated with religious beliefs or mythology. Origins stories are most often literary or legendary; they are typically not historical, in that they are not documented and not considered true by those outside the culture or belief system. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
